onsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3613203\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 20, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gby1665702633390.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gby1665702633390.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gby1665702633390.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gby1665702633390\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame Color</span> widget property determines the color of the frame around the widget, if a frame is specified.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"gby1665702633390__topic_d104108e1_d104109e1_d104110e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gby1665702633390__p_d104111e1_d104112e1_d104113e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>FrameColor<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorName</var> |\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">HexColorNumber</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"gby1665702633390__section_w854ab1b5b3_w855ab1b5_w856ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gby1665702633390__p_d104114e1_d104115e1_d104116e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"FrameColor=midnightblue\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"gby1665702633390__section_w857ab1b5b5_w858ab1b5_w859ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"gby1665702633390__d5952e17\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gby1665702633390__d5952e17__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gby1665702633390__d5952e17__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gby1665702633390__d5952e17__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gby1665702633390__d5952e17__entry__2\">Name of a web color or system color. For more\n                        information, see the \"Standard Colors\" topic.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gby1665702633390__d5952e17__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">HexColorNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gby1665702633390__d5952e17__entry__2\">Hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark) of\n                        a color. For example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">#D90E1A</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gby1665702633390__d5952e17__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">RGBColor</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gby1665702633390__d5952e17__entry__2\">RGB (Red Green Blue) numeric values in the form\n                           <var class=\"keyword varname\">R</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">G</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">B</var>. For example <code class=\"ph codeph\">255,0,0</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gby1665702633390__section_iwx_xzn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d597160e164\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"gby1665702633390__table_d12290e1_d12291e1_d12292e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n                        Frame</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gby1665702633390__section_xmn_c14_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d597160e211\">Drop-Down List and TabEx</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gby1665702633390__p_d104123e1_d104124e1_d104125e1\">By default, if <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame</span> is\n            true, a frame is displayed according to the Windows default or theme. If a valid color\n            is defined for the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame Color</span>, the specified color is used\n            instead of the default.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gby1665702633390__section_apr_214_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d597160e227\">Command Button</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gby1665702633390__p_d104129e1_d104130e1_d104131e1\">For command buttons, this property is supported\n            only when the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Representation</span> property is set to\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">Uniface</code>. The default frame color is black, but you can use the Frame\n            Color property to set it to another color.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gby1665702633390__p_d104132e1_d104133e1_d104134e1\">However, if <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame Type</span> is\n            set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">3D</code>, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Frame Color</span> is applied only when\n            the command button has focus.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gby1665702633390__section_bh5_h14_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d597160e254\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"gby1665702633390__ul_ot5_j14_wwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gby1665702633390__li_d41741e1_d41742e1_d41743e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrc1665702631553.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrc1665702631553.html\" title=\"The CommandButton is a logical widget that enables a user to initiate an action by clicking the button.\">CommandButton</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gby1665702633390__li_d41744e1_d41745e1_d41746e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fud1688450548955.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fud1688450548955.html\" title=\"The udropdownlist widget is a field-level widget that can display a list of valid options in a list below the input field, so that the user can select one. It is applicable only to form components.\">udropdownlist (DropDownList)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gby1665702633390__li_d41747e1_d41748e1_d41749e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/svg1665702629592.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Frame</a><p>Determines whether a border is displayed around the widget at run time. True or False. The default value depends on the widget.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xti1665702633239.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Frame Type (FrameType)</a><p>Controls the appearance of the frame around the widget.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rcm1665702587635.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Standard Colors</a><p>Uniface supports standard color definitions including system colors as defined by the operating system, Web colors defined by the W3C, and RGB (red-green-blue) colors expressed in hex or decimal numbers. Any of these color definitions can be used when defining the value of foreground and background colors of components, widgets, panels, and toolbars.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613203\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613203\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Frame Color (FrameColor) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The Frame Color widget property determines the color of the frame around the widget, if a frame is specified. \" FrameColor = ColorName | HexColorNumber \" Example: \"FrameColor=midnightblue\" Value Description ColorName Name of a web color or system color. For more information, see the \"Standard Colors\" topic. HexColorNumber Hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark) of a color. For example: #D90E1A . RGBColor RGB (Red Green Blue) numeric values in the form R , G , B . For example 255,0,0 Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Frame Drop-Down List and TabEx By default, if Frame is true, a frame is displayed according to the Windows default or theme. If a valid color is defined for the Frame Color , the specified color is used instead of the default. Command Button For command buttons, this property is supported only when the Representation property is set to Uniface . The default frame color is black, but you can use the Frame Color property to set it to another color. However, if Frame Type is set to 3D , the Frame Color is applied only when the command button has focus. Applies To CommandButton udropdownlist (DropDownList) utabex (TabEx) Related Links Frame Determines whether a border is displayed around the widget at run time. True or False. The default value depends on the widget. Frame Type (FrameType) Controls the appearance of the frame around the widget. Standard Colors Uniface supports standard color definitions including system colors as defined by the operating system, Web colors defined by the W3C, and RGB (red-green-blue) colors expressed in hex or decimal numbers. Any of these color definitions can be used when defining the value of foreground and background colors of components, widgets, panels, and toolbars. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}